-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
-- seed_exercises.sql
-- ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
-- Purpose: populate public.exercises with the shared library
--          (~230 rows) used by every coach.
-- Reference: MIGRATION_PLAN.md §4.2 and §5.3.
--
-- This is a SEED file, not a migration. It lives in
-- supabase/seed/, NOT supabase/migrations/. Run it after
-- migrations 001-021 are applied. Re-running is safe due to
-- ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING.
--
-- Rows have coach_id IS NULL and is_seed = true, making them
-- visible to every authenticated coach via the
-- exercises_select_own_coach RLS policy in 015_rls_exercises.sql.
--
-- ID generation is deterministic: each id is the UUID v5 of
-- (namespace, lower(trim(name))) where
--   namespace = a8e7c4e0-9f2b-4c1d-8e3a-1f5b7d9c2e4a
-- so re-running the seed (or running it on a fresh DB)
-- produces the same ids every time. See the project README
-- for the generation script.

begin;

